#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "{{company_name}} is committed to improving the accessibility and usability of {{website_url}} for all users, including people with disabilities. We aim to provide an inclusive digital experience and continuously work toward enhancing accessibility across our website."
