msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "Based on our internal review, this website is <strong>{{conformance_status}}</strong> with <strong>{{accessibility_standard}}</strong>."
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "This status reflects our evaluation at the time of publication and is based on our internal review and available information. Accessibility is an ongoing process, and conformance levels may evolve as updates are implemented."
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "Accessibility Features"
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "To support accessibility, this website includes the AccessYes accessibility interface. This interface allows users to adjust certain visual and usability settings according to their individual needs, such as:"
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "Text size and spacing adjustments"
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "Contrast and color settings"
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "Highlighting tools"
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "Other assistive viewing options"
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "These tools are intended to improve user experience, but do not replace the need for accessible content and proper underlying website structure."
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "Limitations and Technical Considerations"
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "Please note the following:"
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "The availability and effectiveness of accessibility features depend on the website's configuration and ongoing maintenance."
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "While we strive to ensure accessibility across <strong>{{website_url}}</strong>, some content or features may not yet fully meet the selected accessibility standards. Some content may be provided by third parties or affected by technical constraints beyond our immediate control."
msgstr ""

#: lite/admin/app/src/constants/statement-constants.ts
msgid "Additionally, there may be certain legacy content or integrations that may not yet fully align with the selected accessibility standard. We are actively working to identify and address accessibility barriers within our control."
